    management: "ESR used for monitoring disease activity in temporal arteritis, polymyalgia rheumatica, RA. CRP preferred for acute monitoring. ESR remains valuable for diagnosing temporal arteritis (ESR >50 mm/hr + symptoms = high probability).",
