    examPitfalls: ["Semen must be analyzed within 1 HOUR of collection—motility decreases with time", "Liquefaction should occur within 30 MINUTES—failure to liquefy may indicate prostatic dysfunction", "The first fraction of the ejaculate is the most concentrated—incomplete collection causes falsely low count"],
